# Frontend React

- Light mode; Vercel-like console styling already established.
- Never invent production stats; label demo vs live.
- Distinguish online vs recently seen; completed jobs vs queue total.
- Operator key: sessionStorage + `X-Operator-Key`, never URL query.
- Confirm destructive actions; separate connection vs action errors.
- Semantic tables, focus-visible, skip link, ARIA live for toasts, WCAG AA contrast.
- Globe: real `/dashboard/activity` nodes only; arcs are visualization, not measured traffic.
